precis:
Amendments to the ALBERTA FISHERY REGULATIONS which provide for the
issuance of a Metis commercial fishing licence, exempt certain kinds of
illuminated fishing devices from the general ban on fishing with lights,
and prohibit anglers from combining the Alberta and Saskatchewan catch and
possession quotas applicable to Primrose Lake.
